{"tid":1146063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國貿易代表辦公室通知2,000億美元中國貨品上調關稅措施 明日中午12時生效","createTime":"2019-05-09T04:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T07:04:25.000Z","uid":13663,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2414027913bff490c7244d0d70aa17e6f95bfdbc","tid":1146063,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:28:13.000Z","msg":"美國貿易代表辦公室向美國《聯邦公報》發出通知，宣布美國對2,000億美元中國貨品關稅稅率，由10%上調至25%，於美國時間周五(10日)零時，即本港及北京時間周五正午12時生效，有關公告在今日(9日)的《聯邦公告》中刊登。<br />\n<br />\n國家商務部昨晚(8日)公布，美方擬於5月10日將2,000億美元中國輸美商品的關稅從10%上調至25%，指升級貿易摩擦不符合兩國人民和世界人民的利益，中方對此深表遺憾，如果美方關稅措施付諸實施，中方將不得不採取必要反制措施。(fc/da)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.940418/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.940418%2F2&d=oAUO7kpDmgkuxlfprI4EYcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=9c76de6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.940418/2</a>"},{"pid":"e99abbc2f17fd93093a0a4ab2a1accc450348165","tid":1146063,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:31:03.000Z","msg":"仲有半個鐘 期待今日1:00開市會點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d36f40002206c17c63a51cf12bb1fea38bdff3","tid":1146063,"uid":177039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"準備又加關稅個日爆升返幾百點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c25e142b0a5d537b5b942d05047d3fd2a6de4d","tid":1146063,"uid":13108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"endgame 開場"},{"pid":"9e0a7daabfb2b0838f88cbf632da82b3e1b87e13","tid":1146063,"uid":171446,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fa75f2c6599667146abe41a3492cfd60486174e","tid":1146063,"uid":